• **apt update** Update package list
• **apt upgrade** Upgrade all upgradable packages
• **apt full-upgrade** Upgrade with new package installs (full upgrade)
• **apt install <package-name>** Install a package
• **apt remove <package-name>** Remove a package (keep config files)
• **apt purge <package-name>** Remove a package and config files
• **apt install --reinstall <package-name>** Reinstall a package
• **apt search <keyword>** Search for a package by name
• **apt show <package-name>** Show package info
• **apt list --installed** List installed packages
• **apt list --upgradable** List upgradable packages
• **apt clean** Clean downloaded .deb files (cache)
• **apt autoremove** Remove unnecessary packages
• **apt --fix-broken install** Fix broken dependencies
• **apt-mark showhold** Check for held packages
• **apt-mark hold <package-name>** Hold a package at current version
• **apt-mark unhold <package-name>** Unhold a package
• **apt download <package-name>** Download a .deb file without installing
